3.3 Teknik Pengumpulan Data
Data dikumpulkan menggunakan SQL query kompleks dengan JOIN antar 5 tabel:
```sql
SELECT o.created_at, DATE(o.created_at) order_date, DAYOFWEEK(o.created_at) day_of_week,
       HOUR(o.created_at) order_hour, p.nm_produk, t.name_toping, u.nama ukuran,
       oi.qty, oi.total item_total
FROM orders o JOIN order_items oi ON o.id = oi.order_id
JOIN products p ON oi.product_id = p.id
LEFT JOIN topings t ON oi.toping_id = t.id
LEFT JOIN ukurans u ON oi.ukuran_id = u.id
WHERE o.created_at >= DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL 120 DAY)
```
Data diekstrak via mysql-connector-python ke pandas DataFrame untuk preprocessing.

3.4 Model dan Algoritma Machine Learning

3.4.1 Rekomendasi Menu (Content-Based Filtering + Popularity Score)
Formula popularity score:
```
popularity_score = (order_count × 0.6) + (normalized_revenue × 0.4)
normalized_revenue = total_revenue / max_total_revenue
```
Grouping berdasarkan: day_of_week + menu_name + topping + ukuran

3.4.2 Prediksi Pendapatan Harian (Linear Regression)
Model equation:
```
total_revenue = β₀ + β₁×day_of_week + β₂×expected_orders + ε
```
Training: scikit-learn LinearRegression(), train-test split 80:20
Evaluation metrics: R² Score, MSE

3.4.3 Analisis Pola Musiman (Time Series Analysis)
Komponen analisis:
- Daily aggregation per day_of_week
- Hourly peak detection (top 3 jam per hari)
- Trend calculation: MA-7 comparison (recent vs previous week)
- Seasonal decomposition: trend + seasonal + remainder

